## Instructions

1. Locate clutch cable adjuster near lever.  
2. Loosen lock nut, adjust cable to 2â€“3 mm free play.  
3. Tighten lock nut.  
4. Check lever pull for smooth operation.  
5. Inspect clutch lever pivot and lubricate if necessary.  
6. Test ride to ensure proper engagement/disengagement.
